=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
קדמה  -  קדם / qedem  qêdmâh / keh'-dem, kayd'-maw
=== Etymology ===

From {{HH|6923}}; 
=== Noun ===
the front, of palce (absolutely the fore part, relatively the East) or time (antiquity); often used adverbially (before, anciently, eastward): - aforetime, ancient (time), before, [[east]] (end, part, side, -ward), eternal, X ever (-lasting), forward, old, past. Compare {{HH|6926}}.